I am planning to deprecate the benchmarkfdrData2019 (https://bioconductor.org/packages/benchmarkfdrData2019) ExperimentHub Bioconductor package. The reason is because this package relies heavily on SummarizedBenchmark, which is now deprecated as well (https://bioconductor.org/packages/SummarizedBenchmark).

Following the Bioconductor Package End of Life policies (https://contributions.bioconductor.org/package-end-of-life-policy.html#implementation-detail), I?m notifying the bioc-devel mailing list of the change in status.

All the best,
Stephanie Hicks


