It looks like a bug in the code that was fix in devel but not pushed to release (assuming you are using Bioc 3.20 / R 4.4?  as you did not provide your sessionInfo?)

We will ask the maintainers to fix the release version.

While its not recommended to install from outside BiocManager::install to prevent mismatch and incompatible versions, you could install the updated github branch directly from the maintainer of the package in the meantime:

library(devtools)
devtools::install_github(repo="BioinformaticsFMRP/TCGAbiolinks", ref="devel")



