Please remember,  The Bioconductor 3.20 branch will be frozen Monday March 24th.

After that date, no changes will be permitted ever on that branch.

The deadline for devel Bioconductor 3.21 packages to pass R CMD build and R CMD check is Friday April 11th.  While you will still be able to make commits past this date,  This ensures any changes pushed to git.bioconductor.org are reflected in at least one build report before the devel branch will be copied to a release 3.21 branch.  We will freeze and create the 3.21 branch officially on April 15 in preparation for the April 16th release.

